**Local development (AI Service):**
```bash
cd services/ai
cp .env.example .env
uv sync
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --reload
```

**Local development (WA Engine):**
```bash
cd services/wa-enggine
cp .env.example .env
yarn install
