## 19. Sequence Flow

### Sequence 1: User kirim private chat

```txt
User                    WA Engine                   AI Service              DeepSeek
  |                         |                          |                       |
  |--(1) WhatsApp Message-->|                          |                       |
  |                         |--(2) Parse & Validate    |                       |
  |                         |--(3) Trigger Check       |                       |
  |                         |   (private -> process)   |                       |
  |                         |--(4) Build AI Payload    |                       |
  |                         |                          |                       |
  |                         |--(5) POST /api/chat------>|                       |
  |                         |                          |--(6) Build Prompt     |
  |                         |                          |--(7) Get History      |
  |                         |                          |--(8) Call DeepSeek---->|
  |                         |                          |                       |
  |                         |                          |<---(9) AI Response ---|
  |                         |                          |                       |
  |                         |<---(10) ChatResponse ----|                       |
  |                         |                          |                       |
  |                         |--(11) Send Reply         |                       |
  |<--(12) Reply Message ---|                          |                       |
```

### Sequence 2: User kirim pesan grup (mention bot)

```txt
User (Group)            WA Engine                   AI Service
  |                         |                          |
  |--(1) Group Message      |                          |
  |    (@bot + text)        |                          |
  |                         |--(2) Parse & Validate    |
  |                         |--(3) Trigger Check       |
  |                         |   (group + mention ->    |
  |                         |    process)              |
  |                         |--(4) Clean Text          |
  |                         |   (remove @mention)      |
  |                         |--(5) Build AI Payload    |
  |                         |                          |
  |                         |--(6) POST /api/chat------>|
  |                         |                          |
  |                         |<---(7) ChatResponse -----|
  |                         |                          |
  |                         |--(8) Send Reply (quoted) |
  |<--(9) Reply Message ----|                          |
```

### Sequence 3: Reconnect / Error handling

```txt
WA Engine
  |
  |-- Connection closed
  |   |
  |   +-- loggedOut / 401 / 403 / bad session?
  |   |     YES -> Reset auth state, clear sessions
  |   |     NO  -> Schedule reconnect (exponential backoff)
  |   |
  |   +-- Inside pairing window?
  |         YES -> Use WA_PAIRING_RECONNECT_DELAY_MS
  |         NO  -> Normal backoff
  |
  |-- Unhandled rejection / exception
  |   |
  |   +-- Recoverable Baileys error (408, 515, timeout)?
  |         YES -> Schedule reconnect
  |         NO  -> process.exit(1)
```

